elocity Metrics</h3>\n<p class=\"card-body text-on-surface-variant font-body text-[1rem] leading-relaxed line-clamp-2\">\n                        Optimizing delivery pipelines through automated auditing and iterative feedback loops.\n                    </p>\n</div>\n<!-- Card 03 -->\n<div class=\"card-item bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-lg border border-outline-variant/20 flex flex-col items-start transition-all hover:bg-surface-container duration-300\">\n<div class=\"card-num w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center bg-primary rounded-lg mb-6\">\n<span class=\"text-on-primary font-bold text-sm\">03</span>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"card-title text-on-surface font-headline font-bold text-[1.375rem] mb-4\">Scaled Governance</h3>\n<p class=\"card-body text-on-surface-variant font-body text-[1rem] leading-relaxed line-clamp-2\">\n                        Implementing robust structural standards that maintain creative integrity across global markets.\n                    </p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- Asymmetric Design Element: Bottom Detail -->\n<div class=\"mt-12 flex items-center gap-4 opacity-40\">\n<div class=\"h-px w-24 bg-outline\"></div>\n<span class=\"text-[0.65rem] font-label uppercase tracking-widest font-bold\">Confidential Working Document</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</main>\n<!-- Footer -->\n<footer class=\"bg-[#f9f6f5] dark:bg-zinc-950 flex justify-between items-center px-12 py-8 w-full border-t border-[#afadac]/20 fixed bottom-0\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center gap-6\">\n<span class=\"text-[#2f2f2e] dark:text-[#f9f6f5] font-['Manrope'] text-[0.75rem] font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase\">\n                © 2024 Editorial Precision. All rights reserved. | Slide 04\n            </span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex items-center gap-8\">\n<a class=\"text-[#2f2f2e]/40 dark:text-[#f9f6f5]/40 hover:text-[#2f2f2e] dark:hover:text-white transition-colors font-['Manrope'] text-[0.75rem] font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase\" href=\"#\">Privacy Policy</a>\n<a cla